---
import BaseLayout from "~/layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy" description="Privacy policy for usequickutils.com. All processing happens locally in your browser.">
  <article class="max-w-3xl mx-auto prose prose-sm dark:prose-invert">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-[-0.04em] mb-2">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 mb-8 tracking-[-0.04em]">Last updated: May 2026</p>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold tracking-[-0.04em] mb-3">1. Local Processing Only</h2>
      <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed tracking-[-0.04em] text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
        All utility tools on usequickutils.com operate entirely within your browser using HTML5 Canvas and JavaScript APIs. 
        <strong>No files, text, or data you submit are ever uploaded, transmitted, processed, stored, or cached on any remote server.</strong>
        Every compression, conversion, resizing, and text transformation occurs locally on your device.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold tracking-[-0.04em] mb-3">2. Information We Collect</h2>
      <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed tracking-[-0.04em] text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
        We do not collect, store, or process any personal data, files, or user-generated content. 
        We may use standard third-party services (e.g., Google Analytics, Google AdSense) that set cookies 
        to serve personalized advertisements and collect anonymized usage statistics. These services operate 
        under their own privacy policies.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold tracking-[-0.04em] mb-3">3. Cookies</h2>
      <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed tracking-[-0.04em] text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
        This site may use cookies for analytics and advertising purposes via Google AdSense. 
        You can control cookie preferences through your browser settings. We do not use cookies to 
        track or identify individual users beyond standard aggregated analytics.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold tracking-[-0.04em] mb-3">4. Third-Party Services</h2>
      <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed tracking-[-0.04em] text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
        We use Google AdSense to display advertisements. Google may use cookies to serve ads based on 
        your prior visits to this and other websites. You may opt out of personalized advertising by 
        visiting <a href="https://www.google.com/settings/ads" class="underline" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Google Ads Settings</a>.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold tracking-[-0.04em] mb-3">5. Contact</h2>
      <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed tracking-[-0.04em] text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
        For privacy-related inquiries, contact us at <strong>support@usequickutils.com</strong>.
      </p>
    </section>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
